Package com.cisco.nesal.agent

This packages contains Java classes that provide service for software products to use.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IEntitlementNotificationListener
    This interface represents a listener for receiving EntitlementNotification.
    IMeteredUsageListener
    This interface represents a listener for receiving MeteredUsageNotification.
    ISmartAgentNotificationListener
    This is the interface for receiving Smart Agent notification.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Certificate
    Certificate class contains information of a certificate.
    CSR
    This class represent a Certificate Signing Request (CSR).
    Entitlement
    The Entitlement class provides the interface for an application or feature in software product to request an entitlement (also called a license).
    SmartAgent
    This class represents the Admin and Management services provided by Smart Agent.
    SmartAgentInfo
    This class represents the structured information of the Smart Agent.
    SmartAgentInfo.CertificateInfo
    This inner class of SmartAgentInfo contains certificate information in a data structure.
    SmartAgentInfo.EnableInfo
    This inner class of SmartAgentInfo contains "enable: information in a data structure.
    SmartAgentInfo.EntitlementInfo
    This inner class of SmartAgentInfo contains entitlement information in a data structure.
    SmartAgentInfo.OtherInfo
    This inner class of SmartAgentInfo contains all other related information in a data structure.
    SmartAgentInfo.ScheduledJobInfo
    This inner class of SmartAgentInfo contains scheduled job information in a data structure.
    SmartAgentInfo.StatusInfo
    This inner class of SmartAgentInfo contains status information in a data structure.
    SmartAgentInfo.VersionInfo
    This inner class of SmartAgentInfo contains version information in a data structure.
    SmartAgentNotification
    This class represents a notification from Smart Agent.
    SUDI
    This class represents Secured Unique Device Identifier (SUDI).
    UDI
    UDI/SUDI/VUDI structure.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CSR.CSRFormat
    Output format type of Certificate Signing Request.
    Entitlement.EntitlementEnforceMode
    The enforcement mode to be use for an entitlement.
    SmartAgentInfo.OtherInfo.TransportMode
    The transport to use when sending and receiving messages for.
    SmartAgentNotification.NotificationType
    Notification types used for both entitlement notifications and global notifications.
    SmartAgentStatusCode
    This enum represents the status code that may be returned or contained in the exception after a call to the services provided Smart Agent.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SmartAgentException
    Exception to be thrown when error occurred in License Agent operations.

Package com.cisco.nesal.agent Description

This packages contains Java classes that provide service for software products to use. It includes the followings:
  • Admin & Management API
  • Entitlement API
  • Agent Notification API
